Leading ICT distributor for data centre, enterprise, and cloud solutions, First Distribution presented its cloud brokerage and product stack at the 2018 MyBroadband Cloud, Hosting, and Security Conference, which took place at the Gallagher Convention Centre in Midrand on 13 June. “First Distribution launched Africa’s first cloud brokerage, which allowed for the consolidation of multiple cloud products in one place,” said Jason Sharp, Group Executive at First Distribution. “This is one of the primary tools that allow resellers and specialist integrators to participate in the cloud market for their end users.” The MyBroadband Cloud Conference provides IT executives, managers, and business owners from various industries with a platform to interact and do business with South Africa’s top cloud and hosting providers. For more information, watch the video below of First Distribution at the conference.  This article was published in partnership with First Distribution.